<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>In The Crow: City of Angels, you assume the persona of a lost soul named Ashe, who was ruthlessly gunned down along side his young boy. After you are brought back to the land of the living by a majestical crow, you set out on a vengeance rampage.
                  <br><br>The game consists of various levels ranging from back alleys to bars and clubs. You are presented with a set challenge of making it through each of these sections, facing numerous baddies and thugs, all waiting at a chance to take a swing at your head. And to help make things easier, you have an array of weapons at your disposal to aid you in your quest for revenge and eternal peace. Barrels, bottles, bats, fiery liquor, swords, crowbars, it's all there.
                  <br><br>Can you help Ashe achieve his quest and put him at peace?
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>3-D fighting with a vengeance.
                  <br><br>They killed you. But you came back. An avenging angel from beyond the grave. A vigilante reborn to bring justice to the damned. Take your unearthly powers and wreak vengeance on Judah, L.A.'s drug king, Kali, the nin-jitsu death-bitch, Curve, Spider Monkey and an army of lowlife thugs...
                  <br><br>Because life after death is hell..
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>3D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>SCI-FI & Horror themes.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

